                           <Text fill="WHITE" layoutX="10.0" layoutY="244.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="   When a king is attacked, it is called check. Check can be viewed as saying: ''Watch out! The king is attacked!''. Since a king can never be captured, the term ''check'' is used when a king is threatened. If a player is in check, they must get out of check!" wrappingWidth="953.84375">
