                              </font>
                           </Text>
                           <Text fill="WHITE" layoutX="10.0" layoutY="348.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="   One of the most common ways to end a chess game is by checkmate. This happens when one of the players is threatening the other king and it cannot move to any other squares, cannot be protected by another piece and the checking piece cannot be captured." wrappingWidth="953.84375">
                              <font>
